{"tid":1889894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7.21前夕黑警肺炎，到8.31天滅黑警","createTime":"2020-02-21T00:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T01:05:03.000Z","uid":207087,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f7e280ab13d586c304e091be0ba1ac578c108aac","tid":1889894,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T00:51:50.000Z","msg":"開始集氣"},{"pid":"ebdd32a1caf08da9564d5793c407928800d96cd4","tid":1889894,"uid":954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T00:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8778607a18a03de2724b4fd22207d3589443ba13","tid":1889894,"uid":199670,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T00:56:52.000Z","msg":"831？ 太遲啦  8月5都夠啦<br />\n<br />\nBtw認真睇哂佢plz <br />\n<br />\nTerry Yeung:<br />\n新聞跑來了。「文宣平台」複製貼上，再推農場內容謀利；兩登網友群起轉發，內容被一覽無遺。<br />\n<br />\n點擊沒了，連帶的商業價值都被抹殺。有些媒體，如《蘋果》，更是走會員制。<br />\n<br />\n試問，你忽然尊重的媒體工作者，要怎樣謀生？<br />\n<br />\n半年來，愈見惡化。議題被網民壞習慣，以及網軍的無形之手操控。<br />\n<br />\n然後你說：運動靜咗好多。<br />\n<br />\n改變自己，改變習慣。<br />\n<br />\n1. 不是正統媒體的新聞，不轉發。<br />\n2. 未經Fact Check、來自內容農場的消息，不要理。<br />\n3. 很多文宣大台都是盜取內容，不轉發。<br />\n4. 只轉發原創者的內容<br />\n5. 貼報道上討論區，只取少量內容，放link鼓勵點擊（尢其文宣大台該帶頭做）。<br />\n<br />\n再重覆，目標為上，才可以拯救連登垂死的熱門。<br />\n<br />\n比方說，<br />\n1. 如果兩日後有遊行，專注推行動Post；<br />\n2. 同一議題，集中處理，不要分散；<br />\n3. 有人留言「拉」，網友不需再留言；<br />\n4. 戒除政治J女性癖，不要再討論區議員身材；<br />\n5. 未能Fact Check的事情，忍痛讓佢沉。<br />\n6. 減少用極端字眼，例如「就嚟輸」；<br />\n7. 至為重要：不 要 再 推 假 標 題<br />\n<br />\n每個手足都有責任打好呢場資訊戰，改變習慣，重奪輿論主導權，大家一定做得到。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube戰線：黃色資訊片一律Coment+Like+Share&amp;Subscribe（CLS)（share做唔到的話重要片先share)<br />\n<br />\n香港人，改變。<br />\n<br />\nP.S.如果覺得有意思，煩請分享，謝謝你。<br />\n-------------------------------------------<br />\nIG：Terry_yeung_blog<br />\nIG連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IMS6HI&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqF2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=7d556ee7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI</a>"},{"pid":"530ed8b04c16877f745fee3b7ed6f544272c3cfd","tid":1889894,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T01:04:32.000Z","msg":"鬼唔望佢老母臭肺炎"},{"pid":"001794bbd58dbf1d72683b53e7ed24bb7f97747a","tid":1889894,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T01:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}